    • Class io.github.kensuke1984.anisotime.RaypathCatalog extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      6217165062016323038L

      • 直列化されたフィールド

        • MINIMUM_DELTA_P

          double MINIMUM_DELTA_P
          Minimum value of δp (ray parameter). Even if similar raypaths satisfying RaypathCatalog.D_DELTA are not found within this value, a catalogue does not have a denser ray parameter than the value.

        • WOODHOUSE

          io.github.kensuke1984.anisotime.Woodhouse1981 WOODHOUSE
          Woodhouse formula with certain velocity structure

        • D_DELTA

          double D_DELTA
          This value is in [rad].

          We compute epicentral distances Δ(P)i (P or PcP) and Δ(S)i (S or ScS) for ray parameters pi (pi < pi+1) for a catalogue. If δΔi (|Δi - Δi|) < this value, both pi and pi+1 are stored, otherwise either only one of them is stored.

        • DELTA_P

          double DELTA_P
          Standard δp (ray parameter). In case the δp is too big to have Δ satisfying RaypathCatalog.D_DELTA, another value (2.5, 1.25) is used instantly.

        • raypathList

          java.util.TreeSet<E> raypathList
          List of stored raypaths. Ordered by each ray parameter p.

        • MESH

          ComputationalMesh MESH
          Mesh for computation

        • pDiff

          Raypath pDiff
          Raypath of Pdiff

        • svDiff

          Raypath svDiff
          Raypath of SVdiff

        • shDiff

          Raypath shDiff
          Raypath of SHdiff
